interventions.name: N-803

arms.label: Treatment (venetoclax, rituximab, nivolumab)
arms.description: Patients receive venetoclax PO QD on days 1-28, nivolumab IV over 30 minutes on days 2 and 15 of cycles 1-4 and day 1 of each subsequent cycle, and rituximab IV on day 2 of cycle 1 and day 1 of cycles 2-6. Patients undergo a bone marrow biopsy and blood sample collection as well as PET/CT and CT or MRI during screening and on the trial.

arms.label: Treatment
arms.description: Participants will undergo a bone marrow harvest in the operating room to obtain bone marrow cells. Cells will be isolated and purified utilizing the CliniMacs device.
